Spring_Core_java

Open JavaConfigDemoApp : Use SportPackageInterconnectConfig in place of xml file.
This is java based configuration.
Check out for @Configuration and @ComponentScan Annotations.
Close JavaConfigDemoApp: Rest works same as Annotations based.

Open SwimJavaConfigDemoApp : Use SportConfig in place of xml file.
This is java based configuration.
Check out for @Configuration and @PropertySource Annotations.
@Bean*** is used over methods, and method names are used as string to get beans from the annotation context.
Close SwimJavaConfigDemoApp

Debug the main method, to learn more.

***@Bean
@Bean annotation indicates that the annotated method produces a bean to be managed by the Spring container
Other important Annotation used in spring
https://www.baeldung.com/spring-bean-annotations
